## News

### Nov 2025
UNESCO Toolkit for G20 published — co-authored a policy toolkit on reducing AI-connected inequalities, prepared for the South Africa G20 Presidency.

### Nov 2025
CAISA published research briefs on AGI and its societal implications and a modular approach to digital sovereignty in Denmark.

### May 2025
Appointed Chief Scientist at CAISA during the centre's official launch.


